platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 最高評価のタワーディフェンスゲーム

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The unstoppable, poppable Bloons series gets better with each installment, and this entry in the cute-but-cunning tower-defense franchise is no exception. Bloons TD 5 is adorable and quirky, but there’s an astonishing amount of content, tactical depth, and replayability to go along with the goofy weapons, helium-filled interlopers, and priceless monkey business.
